o share with him in it, there being none coming up with him. (Msb.) It is applied to a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That outstrips;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabuwqN","text_ar":"سَبُوقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, Msb, TA: *) and the pl. [masc., i. e. pl. of the former,] applied to horses is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sub~aqN","text_ar":"سُبَّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [fem., i. e. pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiqapN","text_ar":"سَابِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawaAbiqu","text_ar":"سَوَابِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [or]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawaAbiqu","text_ar":"سَوَابِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiqN","text_ar":"سَابِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"regarded as a subst. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAhilN","text_ar":"كَاهِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAribN","text_ar":"غَارِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of which the pls. are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawaAhilu","text_ar":"كَوَاهِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gawaAribu","text_ar":"غَوَارِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham p. 46.) ―         -b2-  By the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiqaAt","text_ar":"سَابِقَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned in the Kur lxxix. 4 are meant"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The angels that precede the devils with the revelation"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that they convey"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the prophets:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the angels that precede the jinn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"genii, in listening to the revelation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the angels that precede with the souls of the believers to Paradise"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, Jel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and with the souls of the unbelievers to Hell:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that precede in battle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Zj, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the souls of the believers, that go forth with ease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the stars"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that precede other stars"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [See more in the Expositions of Bd and others.]) ―         -b3-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sub~aqN","text_ar":"سُبَّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to palm-trees, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That produce their fruit early."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","T","K","Bd","Jel","Zj"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}